extends layout

block content
  // Bootstrap core CSS
  link(href='vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
  // Custom fonts for this template
  link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:200,200i,300,300i,400,400i,600,600i,700,700i,900,900i', rel='stylesheet')
  link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:300,300i,400,400i,700,700i,900,900i', rel='stylesheet')
  link(href='vendor/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
  // Custom styles for this template
  link(href='css/coming-soon.min.css', rel='stylesheet')

  .overlay
  video(playsinline='playsinline', autoplay='autoplay', muted='muted', loop='loop')
    source(src='mp4/bg.mp4', type='video/mp4')
  .masthead
    .masthead-bg
    .container.h-100
      .row.h-100
        .col-12.my-auto
          .masthead-content.text-white.py-5.py-md-0
            h1.mb-3 [ D-MeetUp ]
            h2.mb-3 Coming Soon!
            p.mb-5
              | Blockchain 기반의 meetup 사이트 구축을 목표로 하는 dApp 프로젝트 입니다.
              strong 2018년 09월
              | ! 서비스 오픈 예정입니다.
            //- .input-group.input-group-newsletter
            //-   input.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Enter email...', aria-label='Enter email...', aria-describedby='basic-addon')
            //-   .input-group-append
            //-     button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button') Notify Me!
  .social-icons
    ul.list-unstyled.text-center.mb-0
      li.list-unstyled-item
        a(href='#')
          i.fa.fa-twitter
      li.list-unstyled-item
        a(href='#')
          i.fa.fa-facebook
      li.list-unstyled-item
        a(href='#')
          i.fa.fa-instagram
  // Bootstrap core JavaScript
  script(src='vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js')
  script(src='vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
  // Custom scripts for this template
  script(src='js/coming-soon.min.js')
